4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with in-demand skills in technologies like JavaScript and Python. The program lasts for 18 weeks, featuring 3 classes weekly with a low student-to-teacher ratio of 7:1. Students will learn to build websites, develop algorithms, utilize APIs, and create their own projects, culminating in hands-on experience. No prior coding skills are necessary, and courses are available in English or Spanish. Graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more details, visit the website: [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop